<h2 id="036">0.36</h2>

<h3 id="notifications-2">Notifications</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Kong Enterprise 0.36</strong> inherits from <strong>Kong 1.2.1</strong> with some exceptions:
    <ul>
